transition-DEFAULT: transition-property: color, background-color, border-color, text-decoration-color, fill, stroke, opacity, box-shadow, transform, filter, backdrop-filter;
transition-colors: transition-property: color, background-color, border-color, text-decoration-color, fill, stroke;
